}\n= {450 Ă— 100 Ă— 2}/{1000 Ă— 9}\n= ?2 %\n9, 2, 10","In how much time, the interest on sum of money â‚¹ 800 at 8 % annual rate of will the interest be â‚¹ 1056?\nI = A - P\n= 1056 - 800 = â‚¹ ?0\nt = {I Ă— 100}/{Pr}\n= {??0 Ă— 100}/{?1 Ă— ?2}\n= ?3 years\n256, 800, 8, 4"]}]},{"type":"numberInput","id":"find-missing-2","label":"Intext Questions 9.2","data":{"isSentence":true,"fontSize":"1rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","title":"Find the compound interest and amount in the following problems.","list":["P = â‚¹ 5000\nRate % annual = 10%\nTime (t) = 2 years\nConversion period = annually\nA = P ~!( 1+ r/100 ~!)^n\n= ?0 Ă— ~!( 1 + ?1/100 ~!) ?2~\n= ??0 Ă— ~!( ?3/?4 ~!) ??2~\n= ??0 Ă— ?5/?6\nA = â‚¹ ?7 ##<mul, 121, 5>\nC = A - P\n= ??7 - ??0 = â‚¹ ?8\n5000, 10, 2, 11, 10, 121, 100, 6050, 1050","P = â‚¹ 7000\nRate % annual = 10%\nTime (t) = 1 year\nConversion period =  half yearly\nn = ?0 , r = ?1 %\nA = P ~!( 1+ r/100 ~!)^n\n= ?2 Ă— ~!( 1 + ??1/100 ~!) ??0~\n= ??2 Ă— ~!( ?3/?4 ~!) ??0~\n= ??2 Ă— ?5/?6\nA = ?7/4 ##<mul, 441, 7>\n=  â‚¹ ?8 ##<div, 30870, 4>\nC = A - P\n= ??8 - ??2 = â‚¹ ?9\n2, 5, 7000, 21, 20, 441, 400, 30870, 7717.50, 717.50","P = â‚¹ 2000\nRate % annual = 5%\nTime (t) = 1 year\nConversion period =  half yearly\nn = ?0 , r = ?1/?2 %\nA = P ~!( 1+ r/100 ~!)^n\n= 2000 Ă— ~!( 1 + ?3/200 ~!) ??0~\n= 2000 Ă— ~!( ?4/?5 ~!) ??0~\n= 2000 Ă— ?6/?7\nA = ?8/4 ##<mul, 1681, 5>\n=  â‚¹ ?9 ##<div, 8405, 4>\nC = A - P\n= ??9 - 2000 = â‚¹ ?10\n2, 5, 2, 5, 41, 40, 1681, 1600, 8405, 2101.25, 101.25","P = â‚¹ 500\nRate % annual = 20%\nTime (t) = 9 months\nConversion period =  Quarterly\nn = ?0 , r = ?1 %\nA = P ~!( 1+ r/100 ~!)^n\n= ?2 Ă— ~!( 1 + ??1/100 ~!) ??0~\n= ??2 Ă— ~!( ?3/?4 ~!) ??0~\n= ??2 Ă— ?5/?6  ##<mul, 441, 21>\nA = ??5/?7 \n=  â‚¹ ?8 ##<divDecimal, 9261, 16, 2>\nC = A - P\n= ??8 - ??2 = â‚¹ ?9\n3, 5, 500, 21, 20, 9261, 8000, 16, 578.81, 78.81","P = â‚¹ 2500\nRate % annual = 20%\nTime (t) = 6 months\nConversion period =  Quarterly\nn = ?0 , r = ?1 %\nA = P ~!( 1+ r